      • getObjByGuiId

        GUILinks2BO getObjByGuiId(java.lang.String guiId)
        This will take the guiId and return the Object of that guiId. If the guiId is not there then it will return null.
        Parameters:
        guiId - The guiId.
        Returns:
        Will return the GUILinks2 Data object of the gui id passed in.

      • getObjByRunBasisLodCcprojCcmodelIds

        GUILinks4BO getObjByRunBasisLodCcprojCcmodelIds(java.lang.String id)
        This will concatenate "RunBasis_ID CCProject_ID CCModel_ID" id's from the Gui_Link4.table and match with the id and return the object which is matched. If the id is not there then it will return null.
        Parameters:
        id - The id value for "RunBasis_ID LOD_ID CCProject_ID CCModel_ID".
        Returns:
        Will return the gui link object.
